        <item>
            <title>《小朋友齐打交》真人版电影，预告片抢先睇 + 或于 2025 年上映</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/09/16/little-fighter/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=little-fighter</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/09/16/little-fighter/fun-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Pickle Rick]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Mon, 16 Sep 2024 07:40:00 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[科技新闻]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[小朋友齐打交]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[小朋友齐打交 2]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[试当真 Trial & Error]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1263298</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">经典动作游戏《小朋友齐打交》或即将以真人电影形式呈现。香港游戏开发者小熊（Marti Wong，王国鸿）及 YouTube 频道「试当真 Trial &amp; Error」都有公布消息，并推出预告影片，预计电影或于 2025 年上映。</p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_86802"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/m1orzYYvFko?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p style="text-align: center;">▲《小朋友齐打交》预告片「试当真 Trial &amp; Error」制作</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">《小朋友齐打交》预告片「试当真 Trial &amp; Error」制作，并与「天下一电影」合作。预告片长 48 秒，以一句「小时候，我们为了甚么而战？」引人遐想，但并未透露任何电影画面。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">《小朋友齐打交》系列在 1995 年首次登场，游戏以其简单易上手的玩法和独特的格斗风格迅速风靡。游戏创始人小熊早前透露《小朋友齐打交 2》（Little Fighter 2，LF2）复刻版的开发进度，并预计于 2024 年圣诞节在 Steam 上推出。</p><p>资料及图片来源：<a href="https://gnn.gamer.com.tw/detail.php?sn=273858">巴哈姆特</a></p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/08/26/utm-se-pc-emulator-windows-xp/tips-2/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【教学】iPad / iPhone 运行 Windows XP 实试　PC 模拟器玩《小朋友齐打交 2》</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/09/16/little-fighter/fun-tech/">《小朋友齐打交》真人版电影，预告片抢先睇 + 或于 2025 年上映</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
